request.description:
7.	Implement appropriate REST methods to allow update of specific records.
a.	The column ‘ID’ is not amendable in any case
b.	If customer is a corporate, then column ‘Number of Shares’ is not amendable
c.	When amending column ‘Number of Shares’ or ‘Share Price per unit’, you need to recompute column ‘Balance’

JSON E.G :

[
    {
        "customerID": "C11233",
        "customerType": "Individual",
        "dateOfBirth": "16/09/1994",
        "mailingAddress": {
            "addressLine1": "13",
            "addressLine2": " Sadally",
            "townCity": "vacoas",
            "country": "Mauritius"
        },
        "contactDetails": {
            "contactName": "Mr Nabeel",
            "contactNumber": "59028747"
        },
        "sharesDetails": {
            "numShares": " 120000",
            "sharePrice": "11.0",
            "balance": "117311.5"
        }
    }
]
